  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbb\u0d9c\u0dbd \u0db6\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda \u0dad\u0dc0\u0db8\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc1\u0dcf\u0dbd \u0da2\u0db1\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A large crowd is still on the ground of struggle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The people are still standing in front of the presidential secretariat where the activists have been continuously struggling for 93 days.",
        "So far, he has also given the people the opportunity to climb the steps of the President's Secretariat."
      ],
